# Keep `railway up` uploads small. The Dockerfiles build from source inside the
# container, so build outputs / deps don't need to be uploaded — and the Python
# agents venv (~320MB) must never be packed into the admin/web build context
# (it was causing the upload to time out).
**/.venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/*.log
